1996;;The Boys Next Door;;American;;John Erman;;Matthew Modine, Nathan Lane, Courtney B. Vance, Mare Winningham;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Boys_Next_Door_(1996_film);;Four intellectually disabled men share a house and are looked after by Jack (Tony Goldwyn), their social worker. The four men try to make sense of a mixed-up world, dealing with everything from runaway rodents to helping Norman (Nathan Lane), who has a new girlfriend (Mare Winningham). Jack's life with his wife is put on hold, and he feels it's time to let them go.